      "role": "user",
      "content": "friend or family? they don't get it. they just say \"it'll get better\" or \"at least you had him for a while\" like that's supposed to help. it doesn't help. it just makes me feel more alone. i'm just so tired of fighting to feel okay when everything feels so empty. it's like i'm just existing in this shell of a house and there's no point to any of it anymore.",
